{"type": "article", "id": 20245, "title": "使用环保材料的葡萄酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-05T07:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104209VZbJmp36s7eW1wGK.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个葡萄酒包装完全使用可回收材料，包装盒的材料源于葡萄皮。盒子的一侧画出了葡萄被分解后的效果，果实变成了葡萄酒，果皮做成了盒子，也是用环保的概念来吸引顾客。包装本身没有太多花哨的地方，在棕色的盒子上印了黑色的图案，有海报的感觉。盒子的大小紧贴着瓶子，显得简约轻巧。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104207pB8GON5lhwfPTk4I.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104207Xp4QZboPWOSVGEAR.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104208HYONSTFeoJlrM5kR.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5212963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}